<paragraph pageId="4" pageNumber="77">
The specific epithet is from Latin, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">e</emphasis>
(without), 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">collum</emphasis>
